// First STATIC will be drawn first, Next STATIC will Overlay and so on
// ** Will be drawn Top to Bottom

// USAGE: DESIGNATOR;FILL_COLOR;OUTLINE_WIDTH;OUTLINE_COLOR;Opacity(*dead*);Modifier(*dead*)

// DESIGNATOR: STATIC for Ground Objects like Runways/Buildings/Taxiways
// Designators also can be ATC Positions to Color the Area if ATC is Online
// eg. BIKF_TWR;FILL_COLOR;OUTLINE_WIDTH;OUTLINE_COLOR;  for single Positions
// eg. BIKF_APP BIRK_APP;FILL_COLOR;OUTLINE_WIDTH;OUTLINE_COLOR;   for multiple Positions

// FILL_COLOR: Hex Color Code (eg. #FFFFFF for white)
// OUTLINE_WIDTH: How many Pixels Outline should be shown (0 for none)
// OUTLINE_COLOR: Hex Color Code for Outline (eg. #FFFF00 for yellow)

// Coordinates designate Single Points to fill Area within thoose Points
//** Apron / Runup / Immersion **

